data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of Ripon, California! Nestled within a highly sought-after neighborhood, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of small-town charm and modern convenience. This home features an open and inviting floorplan that's perfect for both daily living and entertaining. The master suite features a large bathroom and walk-in closet. The two additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed, sharing a well-appointed bathroom. Whether you need space for family members or a dedicated home office, these rooms offer versatility and comfort. The backyard is a nice size. Enjoy a sense of community, and excellent schools, with easy access to highway, shopping, dining, and recreational amenities. Come take a look at this one today!
